/>\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1774061\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1774061</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cKrX8Hi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcKrX8Hi.png&h=591dc375&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/c0oLx8Y.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fc0oLx8Y.png&h=636ccc01&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bZPuZOZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbZPuZOZ.png&h=aeb037f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xdGhpfF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxdGhpfF.png&h=a7713ea3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/utGAVnk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FutGAVnk.png&h=c2b5ff78&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9AYjCAF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9AYjCAF.png&h=0d8781b0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"da36dc337b2d014be5f38d00c7360f292ddf5c6b","tid":1775041,"uid":77416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T15:20:26.000Z","msg":"學下泛民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n表示對有人持有槍械表示十分遺憾。任何人不論任何動機，絕不應該作出危害執法機構人員的行為。<br />\n<br />\n但政府不應將政治爭議放到執法部門解決，並縱容警隊濫用私刑及暴力，認為政府是破壞本港法治的頭號兇手，重申政治問題應透過政治方法解決，要求特區政府答應民間五大訴求。<br />\n<br />\n原文:<br />\n法律界立法會議員郭榮鏗表示，對有人向終審法院及高等法院投擲汽油彈表示十分遺憾。他說任何人不論任何動機，絕不應該作出危害法庭或司法機構人員的行為。<br />\n<br />\n郭榮鏗批評政府，將政治爭議放到法庭解決，並縱容警隊濫用私刑及暴力，認為政府是破壞本港法治的頭號兇手，重申政治問題應透過政治方法解決，要求特區政府答應民間五大訴求。"},{"pid":"9cec45764924033426a70fc40911305f2ad343fb","tid":1775041,"uid":238920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T15:20:28.000Z","msg":"真手足team kill我我都唔割<br />\n不過要掃返低兩三隻狗條氣先順<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55a4cc194bad4b373edf5cd6b49cd0bcfd